        "description": "Welcome to Haunted Escape, a VR experience that’ll keep you on the edge of your seat! You’ve got one goal: escape the haunted room before the creepy inhabitants get to you. Solve puzzles, avoid terrifying creatures, and make it out alive.\n\nIn Haunted Escape, you’ll encounter some seriously spooky characters—like a Zombie Dog, a dead Joker, and even an eerie Mummy. Each challenge will test your nerves and your puzzle-solving skills. The best part? You can play it alone or with a friend!\n\nThe game offers two modes:\n- Solo Mode: It’s just you against the haunted room—get out before it’s too late!\n- Co-op Mode: Work with a friend to help each other escape. Can you both survive?\n\nKey Features:\n- Play solo or team up in co-op mode.\n- Face off against creepy creatures like Granny, Ghosts, a Zombie Dog, and more.\n- High-quality VR graphics for an immersive, hair-raising experience.\n- Puzzles that challenge your brain while keeping your heart racing.\n- Exclusively available on Oculus Quest.",
